The '''1908 [[VMI Keydets]] football team''' represented the [[Virginia Military Institute]] in their eighteenth ever season of organized football. VMI went 4-2 in a fairly short season under head coach [[C. S. Roller|Charles Roller]].<ref name="VMI">http://www.vmikeydets.com/pdf8/708636.pdf</ref>
