<ref name="VMI"></ref>
*On October 13, when VMI played Staunton Military, Charles Roller was away, being replaced by assistant coach [[Pete Krebs (basketball)|Pete Krebs]], who also coached the [[VMI Keydets basketball|basketball team]] that year.<ref name="VMI2"></ref> *On October 31, VMI's George Cook Ferebee died from a blow to the head during the Keydets game against Roanoke College. The game was stopped immediately when his death was announced, after he was carried away to a nearby hospital.<ref name="VMI3"></ref>
